            <h1>Aptana Studio 3 Beta</h1>
            <h3>The professional, open source development tool for the open web</h3>
            <div class="page-hd-desc">
                Develop and test your entire web application using a single environment. With support for the latest browser
                technology specs such as HTML5, CSS3 and JavaScript; and Ruby, Rails, PHP &amp; Python on the server side. We've
                got you covered!
            </div>
